carbonenginejs/tools-core
========================

Copyright (c) 2026 CarbonEngineJS contributors.

This package contains CarbonEngineJS original code for CCP-compatible index
interoperability, prepared SDE joins, character-library generation, caching,
tool orchestration, and optional HTTP access. Its runtime-sof integration uses
the public CarbonEngineJS runtime boundary. It contains no copied CCP or
CarbonEngine source code.

Fenris Creations (CCP Games) source material, tools, assets, and EVE-related
data remain copyright their original holders. These names are used for
interoperability and provenance context. This project is not affiliated with
